spec_data.Name: python3-backlash
spec_data.Description:
backlash is a standalone version of the Werkzeug Debugger based on WebOb
adapted to support for Python3.

backlash has born as a future replacement for WebError in upcoming
TurboGears2 versions.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 11:55:33 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Standalone WebOb port of the Werkzeug Debugger with Python3 support meant to replace WebError in TurboGears2
